        "1655868348d34715f4-0": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "CAN I CANCEL MY ORDER?",
            "content": "<p>If your order has not yet been picked and packed you are able to request a cancellation. Please email: <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>customers@iamsol.com.au</strong></span><strong> </strong>and make sure to quote your order number.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": true
          }
        },
        "1655868348d34715f4-1": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "I JUST PLACED AN ORDER, WHERE IS MY EMAIL CONFIRMATION?",
            "content": "<p>In most circumstances it is more than likely sent to your spam folder or the email address has been incorrectly spelled or you used a different email to your normal, please email <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>hello@iamsol.com.au</strong></span><strong> </strong>with your name and order number after checking this. Our team will amend this for you as soon as possible to ensure you receive all tracking updates.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "9891166a-7648-4555-84e2-cfb0e9832a21": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "CAN I PURCHASE/PICK UP ITEMS FROM YOUR WAREHOUSE?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, please select pick up at checkout. Once packed, you will receive an email to confirm and be contacted to confirm a pickup time.</p><p>Please do not turn up without a confirmed time; otherwise, you may turn up to a closed warehouse.</p><p>Email: <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>customers@iamsol.com.au</strong></span> to organise pick up time.</p><p>Warehouse location is: Broadbeach , GOLD COAST , QLD , 4218</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "18680409-0b8f-43b1-97dc-07c8957da9f8": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "CAN I MAKE AN AMENDMENT TO MY ORDER?",
            "content": "<p>We will do our best to make any changes to your order before dispatch but unfortunately we cannot guarantee this is possible. Please email us within 1 hour of placing your order to ensure the best chance of our team to make any relevant updates to an item or postal address. (This excludes weekends. We will reply to your emails first available opportunity on Monday morning). There may also be other delays which will prevent us from making amendments in time such as over public holidays and sales periods.</p><p>We apologise for the inconvenience and hope to be able to offer this in the future. </p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "content_AG6CUJ": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "WHAT ARE YOUR PAYMENT OPTIONS?",
            "content": "<p>iamsol accepts payment via Amex, Visa, Mastercard, PayPal, Afterpay and Zip Pay. Gift Cards and Credit notes can also be used.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "content_page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        }
